text: Dianela Fría (born 8 July 2000) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * dianela fria tellez * host-south-korea-scores-first-goal-of-water-polo- worlds * pan-am-games-water-polo-women Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
